---
By: Zoroaster
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 283
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Kindness/Gentleness
---
Always meet petulance with gentleness, and perverseness with kindness. A
gentle hand can lead even an elephant by a hair. Reply to thine enemy with
gentleness. Opposition to peace is sin.
